entries.femaleVariant: Hands, hey, my turn. I got a job for you this time.
You for me? Peculiar…
[Pay] Hope this pays off.
Need to think about it.
Zippin' the eds your way now. And I expect results, Hands.
Pending MaxTac convoy – need to know the route it'll take.
Need a 'runner – kind with unique abilities.
Next MaxTac prisoner transport to Los Padres – need to know the convoy's route.
MaxTac. Prisoner. Los Padres? Interesting.
Stakes too high for comfort? Can always find help elsewhere.
Did I say they were?
I have a contact. One capable of extracting the information you require. For the right price.
So listen – trusted 'runner, you of all folks gotta have one on your payroll. Someone for... "special" jobs?
Special meaning high-risk? Out with it, V, declare your need.
Next MaxTac prisoner convoy. Direction – Los Padres. Need the route ASAP.
Los Padres… Well, what you're planning is rather apparent, then.
Fifteen thousand. Though... in light of our lucrative relationship thus far, I'm feeling rather generous. Ten thousand – a rare discount. Agreed?
Fifteen thousand. Non-negotiable. Still interested?
[Pay] Deal.
Need to give it a think.
Need to think over my options, yeah? Buzz you back once I do.
Understandable. Let me know at your leisure. After all, you're pressed for time, I am not.
You've decided, then?
[Pay] Get to work.
Need to think about it some more.
[Pay] Get to work.
Gonna give it another think.
Need a bit more time to mull it over.
This is not a helpline, V. Call me when you make up your mind, and not a moment earlier.
V?
Hands, callin' back about our MaxTac convo.
So, what's this you got for me?
V, you're Dorothy. Dropped into a foreign land, you've faced many obstacles and overcome them to see Hansen's Emerald City.
You made me a wealthier man, V. You raised the Animals' hackles, too. Kudos
I respect those who make an impression. In the event of more work, I'll know the number to call. Contract closed.
Bravo, V. You're a virtuoso – in the art of failure.
The contents of that vehicle – highly valuable. But "someone" reduced it to nothing. Expect payment to be reduced to the same.
Hello, V. Van on the loose, it needs retrieving. Coordinates provided. Head there. Quite simple as these things go.
Except you should expect Animals prowling. Likely feral. Details attached.
Yes?
Mr. Hands? Name's V. Heard you're the one to see about any and all work in Pacifica.
Nice opening. Foot in door through flattery – reliable.
So, how might we help each other?
Need to make contact with the Voodoo Boys' chief, if you can swing it.
Ah, straight to biz, ultra heavy variety.
V is calling. Ergo, V is well.
Need to make contact with the Voodoo Boys' chief, if you can swing it.
The Voodoo Boys – led by one Maman Brigitte. It's no easy feat getting an audience with her.
Don't do biz with 'em?
Thought you could arrange anything.
"Maman Brigitte"? Nickname or cover?
Hm, yeah, didn't expect you could swing this anyway...
V! Reverse psychology? On me? Surely you're better than that…
Really not doin' biz with the Voodoos?
Surprised? I strive to avoid risk in my dealings. They pose much of it.
Still, feelers I can extend. No harm in asking around. I just need information from you – a springboard, if you will.
Sorry, it's personal.
Got somethin' they want.
Sorry, private matter.
Desirable as it may be, privacy won't help you here.
Let's say there's somethin' I got that they want.
You've something for the VDBs? Trust me – they don't want it, they don't need it.
An insular bunch all 'round. Tech, networks, what you will – all in-house. Buuut if you insist...
V? It's your lucky day. If you're serious about making headway in Pacifica, that is.
Work some magic for me?
What's the gig?
OK, who's my contact?
Gig – any hints on what it might be?
Does it matter? Will it sway you? It's clear you don't intend to refuse.
You'll learn all in due course.
Besides, I didn't ask. Getting a word out of the Voodoos is like pulling alligator teeth – painful for everyone involved.
OK, so who do I contact next?
Church, Sloan Lane, inside by the altar. They'll know to look for you.
Got it. Thanks, Hands.
This fuckin' guy... Says he ain't in touch, but fear not! They're just a call away!
He is the only fixer in Pacifica.
Not like they can just blow him off.
A moment, please.
I'll poke around. In the event of a twitch, you'll hear from me.
V? It's your lucky day. If you're serious about making headway in Pacifica, that is.
Work some magic for me?
As I said, whatever you're offering, the VBoys could not, I quote, "give a shit." You kept the your receipt, I trust.
Yet a counteroffer was forthcoming – a gig. Successful completion thereof could earn you an audience with Brigitte.
Maman Brigitte? That a nickname? Spooky cult alias?
Alas, I've not had the pleasure of asking her over tea.
But no. Many assume otherwise, yet her title carries no religious weight.
The Voodoos don't adhere to their cultural heritage. Rather, they loosely allude to it.
As I said, whatever you're offering, the VBoys could not, and I quote, "give a shit." You kept the receipt, I trust.
Yet a counteroffer was forthcoming – a gig. Successful completion thereof could earn you an audience with Brigitte.
Transfer received.
I'm sending the coordinates. Be there in... Bear with me...
Ten hours. The datashard will be waiting.
Encrypted, naturally. Accessible to you based on biometric identification.
Oh, and do your utmost not to make a mess of this, V. I despise cleaning up after others.
Thanks. Later, Hands.
Commit, V – to a decision or to hanging up.
If you're expecting me to guess…
When can we meet? Y'know, face to face?
Perhaps never. Perhaps tomorrow. When it proves absolutely necessary. Not before.
Not lookin' for new chooms, are ya.
V, I offer you what no "choom" can – honesty. Consistent, reliable honesty.
OK, gotta go.
Likewise. Time is eddies.
Heard NetWatch is on the prowl, sniffin' around here lately.
Voodoos' troubles keepin' you up at night? Mr. Hands the altruist.
No, disruptions to the status quo keep me up at night. My concern grows when the seeds of chaos are sown. It's bad for business.
Heard about you, y'know. Some call you the Last Corpo in Pacifica.
Do they, now. And where did this come up? On the NUSA's endangered species list?
Heard it in a past life.
Ah, we all have one, don't we. Isnt' that right, Last Assistant to Arthur Jenkins?
Tell me, Hands – how'd Pacifica wind up in your, well… y'know?
Where most see a lost cause, I see potential for growth.
Not anymore. People seldom realize how much actually goes on here.
V, welcome to Pacifica.
Wow, immediate contact? Outta nowhere? Kinda creepy.
It's called courtesy. I'lll be in touch.
Hello, the name is Hands, Mr. Hands. If you're looking for work in Pacifica, I'm the man to call.
I'm V. No "nice to meet you"?
All right. How very nice to meet you.
If you have business, you know my number.
When do we meet?
Trade in Pacifica – how'd you wind up controlling it?
Heard about you…
Need your help. 'Bout a MaxTac convoy.
Said you have somethin' for me.
Heard NetWatch is a problem – they're meddling in Pacifica.
Gotta go.
I'm certain I have no idea what you're talking about. Unfortunately, this thing I know nothing about is a problem for the VDBs. So much so, district power consumption has dropped by half.
Never mentioned you operate outta Dogtown.
So, your ties to Dogtown – never mentioned 'em before. How come?
Only toward a happy conclusion. You've labored diligently and earned your reward – your very own silver slippers.
Just gimme my fuckin' reward.
Who are you in this fairy tale?
Christ, Hands, if ya got somethin' for me, just hand it over.
Got all the parts cast, dont'cha. What's your role in the story?
Right, well, your "silver slippers" await outside. I wish you safe travels, V. It's been… interesting if not to say peculiar.
Ugh, a man tries to introduce a little culture into this boorish world, and this is the thanks he gets…
Why, the narrator, of course.
Figured as much…
'M I gettin' somethin' or not?
Silver slippers?
By "silver slippers" you mean…
A fitting end to our tale. Something that will spirit you home safely. You'll know what I mean when you see what I'm talking about – soon.
So that's it for our biz together?
Who can say? For the time being it certainly is. Please, no tears… And one last thing – be wary of witches, the wicked and the good. Until next time, V.
Yep, till then, Hands.
Pacifica's a lost cause?
Honestly, V? I never intended to share even that. I trust it's obvious why.
Info like that gets out, could hurt biz?
Bravo.
Yeah, earned my silver slippers, I'd say. Lemme have 'em.
Always excited to get a pair of new kicks. Or whatever we're talkin' about.
Hm, I do appreciate an open mind.
A'right, Hands, 'nough's enough.
Metaphor's esoteric, at best. Goin' anywhere with it?
But do know this deed has no bearing on our arrangement. You still desire entry into the Black Sapphire? Simply settle the tasks that will strengthen my position in Dogtown.
Though this contract will not affect your terms of entry into the Sapphire, I hope to see your best.
